fields.name: DIVISOR
fields.comment: What we should divide the inventory number by

fileTabs.content:
SELECT 
    * 
FROM 
    (SELECT 
        *,
        row_number() OVER(PARTITION BY SRC_SYS_CD, SRC_TBL_NM, MATL_NUM, PLNT_CD, SLOC_CD, BTCH_NUM, BTCH_STS_CD, SPCL_STCK_IND, 
        PRTY_NUM 
        ORDER BY SRC_SYS_CD, SRC_TBL_NM, MATL_NUM, PLNT_CD, SLOC_CD, BTCH_NUM, BTCH_STS_CD, SPCL_STCK_IND, 
        PRTY_NUM) rank_no
    FROM
        in0) a
WHERE rank_no = 1

expression.expression: CASE WHEN length(Trim(lipbin)) = 0 OR lipbin IS NULL THEN '#' ELSE lipbin END
CAST(CASE WHEN TRIM(COALESCE(LILOTS, '')) = '' THEN LIPQOH/'$DIVISOR' ELSE 0 END AS DECIMAL (18,4))
CAST(CASE WHEN TRIM(COALESCE(LILOTS, '')) <> '' THEN LIPQOH/'$DIVISOR' ELSE 0 END AS DECIMAL (18,4))
